test_all_one_range:
assert [1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1] == [1, 1, 1]
  Left contains 3 more items, first extra item: 1
  Full diff:
  - [1, 1, 1]
  + [1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1]
test_all_negative_ones:
assert [-1, -1, -1, -1, -1, -1] == [-1, -1, -1]
  Left contains 3 more items, first extra item: -1
  Full diff:
  - [-1, -1, -1]
  + [-1, -1, -1, -1, -1, -1]
